- **Container Usage**: Use Application container for all dependencies

### ✅ For Users
- **Login Required**: Profile pages now require authentication
- **User Dropdown**: New user dropdown menu with navigation options
- **Search Functionality**: Enhanced search bar in top navigation
- **Mobile Support**: Improved mobile navigation experience

